Vegetable Gardening Encyclopedia: Growing,Freezing,Canning,Storing,Drying 

 Galahad Books 
 1982
 Language: English
 ISBN-10: 0883655942
 ISBN-13: 978-0883655948
 384 pages
 PDF
 14.25 MB

I have used this book for the last 8 years when I do a garden. It almost always has the detail I need for a particular vegetable. Example: My tomato plants look great . The book covers a wide varity of vetables & herbs well. It is very good on basics. It does have a few weaknesses. No interior color pictures, good black & white drawings however. Printed on newsprint. Because of it's age the newer varities are not listed & the ones listed may not be available. It doesn't cover wide beds........................
